<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Baby Name Generator</title>
    <% include ../partials/head.ejs %>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <h1 class="header__title">
            Baby Name Generator
        </h1>
    </header>
    
    <div class="intro">
        <p class="intro__para">
            Are you and your significant other unable to decide on a name for your new baby? <br>
            Did you try to give your baby the most unique name possible and now regret it? <br>
            <span class="intro__small">(name change forms only <a class="intro__link" href="https://info.legalzoom.com/steps-legally-change-name-20369.html" target="_blank">cost about $100</a>)</span><br>
            Let fate decide by using the baby name generator.<br> 
            Customizable by gender, region and total names. <br> 
            You can even generate an email address for your unborn baby!
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="main">

        <form action="/baby" class="main__form" method="post">
            
            <p class="main__group">
                <label for="gender" class="main__label">Gender</label>
                <span class="main__input-wrap">
                   <span class="main__icon-wrap"><i class="fas fa-venus-mars main__icon"></i></span>
                    <select name="gender" id="gender" class="main__select">
                        <option value="male">Male</option>
                        <option value="female">Female</option>
                    </select>
                 </span>
            </p>
            <p class="main__group">
                <label for="region" class="main__label">Country</label>
                <span class="main__input-wrap">
                    <span class="main__icon-wrap"><i class="fas fa-globe-europe main__icon"></i></span>
                    <select name="region" id="region" class="main__select">

                        <% namesArray.map((name) => { %>         
                            <option value="<%= name.region %>"><%= name.region %></option>
                        <% }); %>

                    </select>
                </span>
            </p>
            <p class="main__group">
                <label for="amount" class="main__label">How many names?</label>
                <span class="main__input-wrap">
                    <span class="main__icon-wrap"><i class="fas fa-list-ol main__icon"></i></span>
                    <input type="number" name="amount" id="amount" value="1" min="1" max="100" class="main__input" required>
                </span>
            </p>
            
            <p class="main__group">
               <label for="ext" class="main__label">Email address for your baby?</label>
               <span class="main__radio-wrap">
                    <input type="radio" name="ext" value="yes" class="main__radio">Yes
                    <input type="radio" name="ext" value="no" class="main__radio" checked>No
               </span>
            </p>
            
            
            <div class="main__submit-wrap hay">
                <button class="main__submit">Find Names</button>
            </div>
            
        </form>
        
    </div>
    
    <% include ../partials/footer.ejs %>
    
    <script src="/js/TweenMax.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/ScrambleTextPlugin.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/SplitText.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
    
</body>
</html>